OL,3,CWolverhampton mum pleads people to
OL,4,Cgive up ninja swords before ban
OL,6,FThe mother of a teenager murdered with
OL,7,Fa ninja sword is pleading with people
OL,8,Fto give up their weapons before a ban
OL,9,Fcomes into force so "children can walk
OL,10,Fhome without fear".
OL,12,FA national Surrender and Compensation
OL,13,Fscheme is being launched for ninja
OL,14,Fswords in July, ahead of the ban from
OL,15,FAugust 1.
OL,17,FUnder Ronan's Law, it will be illegal
OL,18,Fto possess, sell, make or import the
OL,19,Fknives.
