OL,3,CWolverhampton mum pleads people to
OL,4,Cgive up ninja swords before ban
OL,6,FThe law is named after 16-year-old
OL,7,FRonan Kanda, who was yards away from
OL,8,Fhis Wolverhampton home when he was
OL,9,Fmurdered with a ninja sword in 2022,
OL,10,Fin a case of mistaken identity.
OL,12,FHis family and mother Pooja Kanda have
OL,13,Fbeen campaigning for the ban since his
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,16,FMs Kanda said: "It has been three
OL,17,Fyears since Ronan's life was
OL,18,Ftragically taken as a result of the
OL,19,Fwounds inflicted by a ninja sword.
OL,26,@xD@POU
