OL,3,CWolverhampton mum pleads people to
OL,4,Cgive up ninja swords before ban
OL,6,F"Since then, we have relentlessly
OL,7,Fcampaigned for ninja swords to be
OL,8,Ftaken off the streets as they have no
OL,9,Fplace in society.
OL,11,F"The Government has now introduced a
OL,12,Fmuch-needed ban on ninja swords, and
OL,13,Fwe encourage those in possession to
OL,14,Fsurrender them to make the community a
OL,15,Fsafer place where children can walk
OL,16,Fhome without fear."
