OL,3,CWolverhampton mum pleads people to
OL,4,Cgive up ninja swords before ban
OL,6,FThe Home Office is also funding 37 new
OL,7,Fsurrender bins, made by charity Word 4
OL,8,FWeapons, across the same locations
OL,9,Fwhere 45% of knife crime in England
OL,10,Fand Wales takes place.
OL,12,FAnyone handing in a ninja sword can
OL,13,Falso claim compensation of #5 ` the
OL,14,Fwholesale price of the weapon ` if
OL,15,Fthey return it to a designated police
OL,16,Fstation.
