OL,3,CWolverhampton mum pleads people to
OL,4,Cgive up ninja swords before ban
OL,6,FPolicing minister Dame Diana Johnson
OL,7,Fsaid: "The launch of today's scheme is
OL,8,Fa result of months of collaborative
OL,9,Fworking with the Coalition to Tackle
OL,10,FKnife Crime and I'm optimistic about
OL,11,Fwhat we can achieve together over the
OL,12,Fnext month and then the years to come
OL,13,Fas part of our plan for change.
OL,15,F"This scheme is just one part of
OL,16,Faddressing knife crime.
OL,18,F"We will not stop listening to those
OL,19,Fwho are directly working with those
OL,20,Fimpacted by this crime."
